{"word":"G1820 - ἐξαπορέομαι - exaporéomai - ex-ap-or-eh'-om-ahee - Despair","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαπορέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exaporéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ap-or-eh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Despair</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நம்பிக்கையற்றுபோ, மனமுறிவடை"},{"paragraph":"to be utterly at a loss, be utterly destitute of measures or resources, to renounce all hope, be in despair"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G639 - ἀπορέω - aporéō - ap-or-eh'-o/639\">G639</a>; to <i>be utterly at a loss</i>, that is, <i>despond:</i> - (in) despair.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}